{"id":3504,"type":4,"name":"Red Dead Redemption","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/73/23/3504_Q97Xc.jpg","rating":{"total":108,"count":{"1":1,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":0,"6":4,"7":13,"8":47,"9":31,"10":11},"score":8.2},"summary":"《荒野大镖客：救赎》（英语：Red Dead Redemption，台港译作“碧血狂杀”）是一款开放世界的西部动作冒险游戏，由Rockstar San Diego开发，Rockstar Games发行。2010年5月18日在PlayStation 3和Xbox 360上发行。它是2004年《红色死亡左轮》的精神继承者。\r\n\r\n游戏的大部分故事发生在1911年，美国旧西部解体之后。游戏的主角John Marston从前是个罪犯，他出发去寻找从前的帮派同伙。Marston的妻儿被政府扣作人质，以迫使他成为一名赏金猎人。Marston别无选择，只能去寻找三名从前的同伴以让他们受到法律的制裁。\r\n\r\n发售之后，该游戏在Metacritic和GameRankings上均得到高分，使得它成为PlayStation 3和Xbox 360平台上最受好评的游戏之一。它的画面、音乐、开放世界的系统、剧情均得到评论家好评。据NPD Sales Group统计，该游戏仅在当年五六月份便卖出200万份。\r\n\r\nsource:https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%92%E9%87%8E%E5%A4%A7%E9%95%96%E5%AE%A2%EF%BC%9A%E6%95%91%E8%B5%8E","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>荒野大镖客：救赎</li><li><span>开发: </span>Rockstar San Diego / Rockstar North、<a href=\"/person/10302\">Rockstar Games</a></li><li><span>发行: </span><a href=\"/person/10302\">Rockstar Games</a></li><li><span>平台: </span>Xbox 360</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PS3</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>动作冒险</li><li><span>游戏引擎: </span>RAGE</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>单人-多人</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2010-05-18</li><li><span>售价: </span>$59.99</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://www.rockstargames.com/reddeadredemption</li><li><span>游戏设计师: </span>Christian Cantamessa et. al.</li>","collection":{"wish":113,"collect":116,"doing":16,"on_hold":23,"dropped":8},"tags":[{"name":"Rockstar","count":26},{"name":"PS3","count":25},{"name":"ACT","count":17},{"name":"XBOX360","count":13},{"name":"R星","count":13},{"name":"西部沙箱","count":11},{"name":"荒野大镖客：救赎","count":8},{"name":"XboxOne","count":5},{"name":"2010","count":4},{"name":"荒野大镖客","count":4},{"name":"西部","count":3},{"name":"弱智AI","count":2},{"name":"TPS","count":2},{"name":"射击感差","count":1},{"name":"枪械科普好游戏","count":1},{"name":"时代の挽歌","count":1},{"name":"16-20","count":1},{"name":"Rockstar_Games","count":1},{"name":"